h2cV8duBQ&oe=66DEDB3E"}, "display_name": "Hololab VR - NCSG Inspection Foundation Module 3: Masonry Wood External", "keywords": [], "long_description": "**Hololab NCSG Wood Burning Freestanding Stoves VR Application**\n\nThe Hololab National Chimney Sweep Guild VR application provides users with essential skills to inspect and maintain wood-burning freestanding stoves in compliance with NCSG standards. This course features interactive slide content, desktop-based activities, realistic simulations, and detailed testing. Users are challenged to perform inspections with randomized issues in a virtual residential setting, ensuring all necessary procedures are followed.\n\n**VR Controls and PPE \u2013** Learn how to navigate the virtual environment while getting acquainted with essential personal protective equipment.\n\n**Responsibility & Worksite Hazard Assessment \u2013** Operate in a simulated environment to identify and mitigate hazards commonly encountered during inspections of wood-burning freestanding stoves.\n\n**Familiarization \u2013** Understand different types of wood-burning freestanding stoves and their common features.\n\n**Freestanding Stove Inspection \u2013** Utilize the official NCSG checklist to thoroughly inspect wood-burning freestanding stoves.\n\n**Real-World Simulation \u2013** Complete the inspection by correctly identifying issues with maximum safety awareness and forensic skills.\n\nData reports for review are saved and stored for engagement metrics and simulation performance analysis.\n\nAny off-platform monetization of content accessible in this app conforms to the Oculus Bulk IAP or Subscription Licenses app policy outlined here: https://developer.oculus.com/policy/app-policies", "short_description": "The Hololab National Chimney Sweep Guild Wood Burning Freestanding Stoves VR application provides users with essential skills to inspect and maintain wood-burning freestanding stoves in compliance with NCSG standards. This course features interactive slide content, desktop-based activities, realistic simulations, and detailed testing."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://ftfvr.com/privacy-app/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "From the Future", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.ftfvr.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "421923165850360"}], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED_FOR_SOME_CONTENT", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8192534080812009"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1481081729498014"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1481081729498014"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1723504696, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1481081729498014"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "8321518367913579", "version": "0.9.299"}, "id": "1153433819285191", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false, "primary_binaries": {"nodes": [{"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7939014966163923", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8321518367913579"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "1153433819285191"}]}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1724947599, "id": "8321518367913